<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3773] Set ZK max connections much higher in 0.90</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3773</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I think by now we can all acknowledge that 0.90 has an issue with ZK connections, in that we create too many of them and it&apos;s also too easy for our users to shoot themselves in the foot.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For 0.90.3, I think we should change the default configuration of 30 that we ship with and set it much much higher, I&apos;m thinking of 32k.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12504101">HBASE-3773</key>
            <summary>Set ZK max connections much higher in 0.90</summary>
